headline: CubeSmart upgraded, Public Storage cut: BMO shifts preference in storage sector
summary: Investing.com -- BMO Capital has shifted its storage REIT preferences, downgrading Public Storage (NYSE:PSA) to Market Perform while upgrading CubeSmart (NYSE:CUBE) to Outperform in a note Friday.
